    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:radial-gradient(at 40% 20%, #7C710C15 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 0%, #6666AD10 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, #C2B86012 0px, transparent 50%), var(--surface-light);background-color:var(--surface-light);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"inset: 0; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; background: var(--texture-grain); opacity: 0.04; z-index: 1\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:72px 44px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #CCCBC0;border-radius:0;padding:22px 20px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7C710C;background:#7C710C18;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:8px;\">CORE DEFINITION</span>\n            <h2 style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#0C0B07;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1.1;\">Narrative Transportation</h2>\n            <div style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:11px;font-style:italic;color:#44433A;margin-bottom:12px;opacity:0.8;\">/\u02c8n\u00e6r\u0259t\u026av tr\u00e6nsp\u0254\u02d0r\u02c8te\u026a\u0283\u0259n/</div>\n            <div style=\"border-left:3px solid #7C710C;padding-left:14px;margin:12px 0 14px;\">\n            <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#0C0B07;margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">The phenomenon where audiences become absorbed into a story, reducing counter-arguing and increasing belief in the message.</p>\n        </div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:Plus Jakarta Sans;font-size:10.5px;color:#44433A;margin:0;line-height:1.4;opacity:0.85;\">Transported audiences are 3x more likely to change attitudes and 2x more likely to take action. Every great carousel transports.</p>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
